Telecom Italia to Sign Broadband Accord With Huawei, Sole Says

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-06-02T07:30:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/telecom-italia-to-sign-broadband-accord-with-huawei-sole-says.html
Telecom Italia SpA (TIT)  will sign a
partnership agreement with Huawei to develop broadband over the
next five years,  Il Sole 24 Ore  reported without saying where it
got the information.  The agreement is part of 14 accords between Italian and
Chinese companies, with a total value of 3.3 billion euros ($4.7
billion), that will be signed tomorrow in Rome, according to the
Italian daily.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
 ssirletti@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  